      <section eId="sec_1_1_3">
        <num>1-1.3</num>
        <heading>Rules governing use of certain words</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1_1_3__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Words in the singular number include the plural, and in the\nplural include the singular.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1_1_3__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Words of the masculine gender include the feminine and the\nneuter, and when the sense so indicates words of the neuter gender may\nrefer to any gender.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1_1_3__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The word "writing" includes typewritten or printed matter.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
